<item>
            <title>[LU-9417] xattr cache memory usage can be reduced</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9417</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;xattr cache refill requests preallocate too large memory buffers as calculated based on maxeadatasize returned by the MDS. If we use smaller buffers, we can reduce memory pressure.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A patch will be uploaded shortly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
